                    <ab>In nomine sancte et individue trinitatis. <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/124">Fredericus</persName> divina favente clementia
                        Romanorum <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> augustus. Dignum duximus
