                            >castello</rs> et <rs key="#Markets">mercatis</rs> et districto, curtem
                        de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/440"><placeName ref="#places/888"
                            >Calliano</placeName></geogName>, curtem de
